## Compatible Tankmates

### Excellent Companions

- **[Cherry Shrimp](/species/cherry-shrimp)** — Coexist without predation issues on adult shrimp. Shrimplets may be at slight risk.
- **[Corydoras](/species/corydoras)** — Different body plans occupy different substrate niches; Corys forage substrate surface while Kuhli Loaches burrow
- **[Neon Tetra](/species/neon-tetra)** — Classic Southeast Asian biotope combination
- **[Betta Fish](/species/betta-fish)** — Often compatible; bettas typically ignore loaches in well-planted setups with ample space
- **[Neocaridina Shrimp](/species/neocaridina-shrimp)** — Generally safe with adult shrimp

### Avoid

- Large cichlids or any fish that will chase and stress loaches
- Goldfish (different temperature range, high flow)
- Any fish known for nipping at slow-moving or elongated bodies

